<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA623_01_IH_0003</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema623_01.css" />
    <script src="../../common_practice/js/ema623_01_ih_0003.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema623_03_ih_0003">
      <section class="title flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
          <span class="title_text" lang="y">『수학 4-1』 평면도형 돌리기</span>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3_orange" lang="y">도형을 시계 반대 방향으로 90°만큼 돌렸을 때의 도형을 그려 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">

          <section class="exercise">
            <h3>③ 도형을 시계 반대 방향으로 90°만큼 돌렸을 때의 도형을 그려 보세요.</h3>
            <div class="shape_grid_area flex align_center">
              <div class="shape-grid">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 390 390" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <defs>
                    <pattern id="grid" width="78" height="78" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                      <path d="M78 0 L0 0 0 78"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#009FE3"
                            stroke-width="1"
                            stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
                    </pattern>
                  </defs>
              
                  <!-- 배경격자 -->
                  <rect width="390" height="390" fill="url(#grid)"/>
              
                  <!-- 1) 그룹으로 묶어서 2) 계산된 tx, ty 만큼 이동 -->
                  <g transform="translate(74.90,75.40)">
                    <path
                      d="M81.0905 2.23438H2.95654V236.967H237.248V80.5154H159.169V158.686H81.0905V2.23438Z"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="#222"
                      stroke-width="4"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                    />
                  </g>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="img_area">
                <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA623_01_IH/0003_02.png" alt="" /> 
              </div>

              <div class="canvas_area">
                <canvas id="gridCanvas"  width="390" height="390"></canvas>
                <!-- 스타일 선택 팝업 -->
                <div id="lineSelectLayer">
                  <button class="to_solid" title="실선"></button>
                  <button class="to_dotted" title="점선"></button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>


        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y" class="text_bullet"></p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
